            "title": "Can Farmers and Bats Co-exist? Farmer Attitudes, Knowledge, and Experiences with Bats in Belize",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Hannah G",
                    "lastName": "Shapiro"
