            "title": "Camera traps unveil demography, social structure, and home range of six unhabituated Western chimpanzee groups in the Moyen Bafing National Park, Guinea",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Benjamin",
                    "lastName": "Debetencourt"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
