            "title": "ROOSTING BEHAVIOR AND ROOST SITE.CHARACTERIZATION OF PTEROPUS VAMPYRUS IN MALAGOS WATERSHED, DAVAO CITY",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ian Evert B",
